cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.GR, cs.MM

This paper is primarily focused on image inpainting, which is a task related to computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also extensively uses deep learning techniques, which falls under the category of machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The paper also discusses the use of texture constraints, which is related to graphics (cs.GR) and the evaluation is done on image datasets (cs.MM).
